-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;9、&amp;nbsp;Plastic&amp;nbsp;Storage&amp;nbsp;Bins（塑料收纳框）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 890px; white-space: normal; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;该产品在过去30天内的营收增长了1911%，消费者对整理归纳类产品的搜索量增长了920%。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 890px; white-space: normal; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.caomaokj.com/storage/article/20221230/1672364953176344.png&quot; alt=&quot;2023年1月亚马逊13大爆款产品预测&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 890px; white-space: normal; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;10、&amp;nbsp;Original&amp;nbsp;Peloton&amp;nbsp;Bike（健身脚踏车）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 890px; white-space: normal; border: 0px; word-br