&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;eBay平台热销品类：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;数码产品、时尚类别，家居及园艺品类，汽配，商业和工业品类。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;eBay卖家注册流程：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;第一步，登陆eBay香港(中国)站点：www.ebay.com.hk点击页面上的注册。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-he