: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;（2）大陆企业：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;·公司名称；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;·企业法人；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;·营业执照号；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;·营业执照副本图片；